hopobject.body: Where do you come from? oi ocha define Smith suspects that the increase in tipped TV injuries is due to the fact that not only are there more TVs, but heavier, older box-shaped TVs are being put in dangerous places like on top of dressers and bookshelves. In cases where the doctors provided details, the number of injuries where a TV fell from a dresser, chest of drawers or armoire increased four times over the time period.
